item.title: Log File1
item.description: So Far So Good? Since I get back into learning mode, I have been doing pretty well. I even started doing Advent of Code, and I have fun doing it. However, it’s not all rainbows and butterflies even though I’ve now regained my ability to really focus for at least a few hours each day. So, what’s the problem? The Problem! The problem is actually twofold. On the one hand, I still have trouble with doing the work.

item.title: Log File0
item.description: A New Start Time flies, and it’s already December 1st. Since this is the beginning of a new month, I want to make some changes to how I approach learning in order to make this month counts. Yes, even though this is the last month of 2024, I just want to size the time I have to actually take my study seriously so that I can become a better version for my next role.
